      <title>随着利率下降的可能性越来越小，阿布扎比重返欧洲债券市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/abu-dhabi-re-enters-eurobond-market-for-first-time-since-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国利率很快下降的预期逐渐减弱，阿布扎比正在出售大约三年来的第一批欧洲债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/abu-dhabi-re-enters-eurobond-market-for-first-time-since-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 06:04:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
